===Colored Conventions===

A description of the person's relationship to the Colored Conventions Movement.-->

==Personal life==

Purnell married Ann Sammons.  Purnell and both were listed as members of St. Thomas's African Episcopal Church, a church of the black elite.  They eventually moved to San Francisco, CA, continuing their civil rights activism. <!--Where did the person live? How did the person spend their free time? Who did the person marry? Did the person have children?-->
